{"ID":"20220906195057-7hza2yn","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20220906195057-7hza2yn","title":"面试问题","type":"doc","updated":"20221118192359"},"Children":[{"ID":"20221010145903-dab8v4h","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20221010145903-dab8v4h","updated":"20221010145911"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"JavaSE"}]},{"ID":"20220906195126-efm5g64","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220906195126-efm5g64","updated":"20221006141800"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"JAVA的优势？别的语言做不到的或者不如他的或者非他不可的？"}]},{"ID":"20220921095528-zzn50u5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220921095528-zzn50u5","updated":"20220921095544"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C++没有垃圾回收，需要自己进行内存管理"}]},{"ID":"20220906195126-jui3013","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220906195126-jui3013","updated":"20220906195126"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"更看好哪个方向？"}]},{"ID":"20220906195126-v4axeg7","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220906195126-v4axeg7","updated":"20220906195126"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"语言和语言之间的过渡？"}]},{"ID":"20220906195126-8v2py2s","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220906195126-8v2py2s","updated":"20220906195126"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"想往哪一方面发展？"}]},{"ID":"20220906195126-z9x2zs3","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220906195126-z9x2zs3","updated":"20220906195126"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"ide快捷键：有个类写多了，如何删除相关所有的错误类？"}]},{"ID":"20221117170344-p0gnwoa","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20221117170344-p0gnwoa","updated":"20221117170355"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Java基本类型"}]},{"ID":"20221120155359-znul39i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120155359-znul39i","updated":"20221120155403"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Properties":{"parent-style":"width: 50%;","style":"width: 10000px;"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/包装类-20220618215622-i8w4mlg.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"width: 10000px;\" parent-style=\"width: 50%;\"}"}]},{"ID":"20221120154234-lxsuxts","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20221120154234-lxsuxts","updated":"20221120154239"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"final修饰变量"}]},{"ID":"20221120154253-12mzwce","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154253-12mzwce","updated":"20221120154253"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"final 修饰的变量即成为常量，只能赋值一次，但是 final 所修饰局部变量和成员变量有所不同。"}]},{"ID":"20221120154304-m7s9fy4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154304-m7s9fy4","updated":"20221120154314"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.final 修饰的局部变量必须使用之前被赋值一次才能使用。"}]},{"ID":"20221120154310-0y9yhmt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154310-0y9yhmt","updated":"20221120154311"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.final 修饰的成员变量在声明时没有赋值的叫“空白 final 变量”。空白 final 变量必须在构造方法或静态代码块中初始化。"}]},{"ID":"20221120154253-lfzcr31","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154253-lfzcr31","updated":"20221120154258"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color8);"},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"注意："},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color8);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"final 修饰的变量不能被赋值这种说法是错误的，严格的说法是，final 修饰的变量不可被改变，一旦获得了初始值，该 final 变量的值就不能被重新赋值。"}]},{"ID":"20221120154403-ygrqqeu","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20221120154403-ygrqqeu","updated":"20221120154413"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"成员变量与局部变量的区别"}]},{"ID":"20221120154403-b6ptf6r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154403-b6ptf6r","updated":"20221120154403"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"1、在类中的位置不同"}]},{"ID":"20221120154403-d1iyh66","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154403-d1iyh66","updated":"20221120154403"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"成员变量：在类中方法外面"}]},{"ID":"20221120154403-aid6e6x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154403-aid6e6x","updated":"20221120154403"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"局部变量：在方法或者代码块中，或者方法的声明上（即在参数列表中）"}]},{"ID":"20221120154403-hk8lykf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154403-hk8lykf","updated":"20221120154403"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"2、在内存中的位置不同，可以看看"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong a","TextMarkAHref":"http://www.cnblogs.com/huangminwen/p/5928315.html","TextMarkTextContent":"Java程序内存的简单分析"}]},{"ID":"20221120154403-395841a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154403-395841a","updated":"20221120154403"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"成员变量：在堆中（方法区中的静态区）"}]},{"ID":"20221120154403-zqow6fn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154403-zqow6fn","updated":"20221120154403"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"局部变量：在栈中"}]},{"ID":"20221120154403-iix0nyo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154403-iix0nyo","updated":"20221120154403"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"3、生命周期不同"}]},{"ID":"20221120154403-akvsm6p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154403-akvsm6p","updated":"20221120154403"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"成员变量：随着对象的创建而存在，随着对象的消失而消失"}]},{"ID":"20221120154403-27mlhks","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154403-27mlhks","updated":"20221120154403"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"局部变量：随着方法的调用或者代码块的执行而存在，随着方法的调用完毕或者代码块的执行完毕而消失"}]},{"ID":"20221120154403-q9mxaem","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154403-q9mxaem","updated":"20221120154403"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"4、初始值"}]},{"ID":"20221120154403-hqtzdny","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154403-hqtzdny","updated":"20221120154403"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"成员变量：有默认初始值"}]},{"ID":"20221120154403-e3gk6zl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154403-e3gk6zl","updated":"20221120154403"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"局部变量：没有默认初始值，使用之前需要赋值，否则编译器会报错（The local variable xxx may not have been initialized）"}]},{"ID":"20221117170355-ngojblh","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20221117170355-ngojblh","updated":"20221117170400"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"链表"}]},{"ID":"20221120161803-91k2cz2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120161803-91k2cz2"}},{"ID":"20221118105633-rnjzm2w","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20221118105633-rnjzm2w","updated":"20221118105642"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"抽象类和接口的区别"}]},{"ID":"20221120154624-vx0u5uw","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20221120154624-vx0u5uw","updated":"20221120154624"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"抽象类（abstract class）："}]},{"ID":"20221120154624-gursek8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154624-gursek8","updated":"20221120154652"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"定义："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"使用abstract修饰符修饰的类。（如果一个类没有包含足够多的信息来描述一个具体的对象，这样的类就是抽象类。）"}]},{"ID":"20221120154624-7pee9vm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154624-7pee9vm","updated":"20221120154624"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"实际点来说，一个抽象类不能实例化，因为“没有包含足够多的信息来描述一个具体的对象”。但仍然拥有普通类一样的定义。依然可以在类的实体（直白点就是能在｛｝里面)定义成员变量，成员方法，构造方法等。"}]},{"ID":"20221120154624-1g0sgvo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154624-1g0sgvo","updated":"20221120154642"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"抽象方法："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"只声明，不实现。具体的实现由继承它的子类来实现。实际点就是：被abstract修饰的方法，只有方法名没有方法实现，具体的实现要由子类实现。方法名后面直接跟一个分号，而不是花括号。例如：public abstract int A();"}]},{"ID":"20221120154624-b7dk6cl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154624-b7dk6cl","updated":"20221120154624"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一个类中含有抽象方法（被abstract修饰），那么这个类必须被声明为抽象类（被abstract修饰）。"}]},{"ID":"20221120154624-v5dayiz","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20221120154624-v5dayiz","updated":"20221120154624"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"接口（interface）："}]},{"ID":"20221120154624-7y6ky7k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154624-7y6ky7k","updated":"20221120154634"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"定义："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"接口在java中是一个抽象类型，是抽象方法的集合。一个类通过继承接口的方式，从而继承接口的抽象方法。从定义上看，接口是个集合，并不是类。类描述了属性和方法，而接口只包含方法（未实现的方法）。"}]},{"ID":"20221120154624-dr1nsja","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154624-dr1nsja","updated":"20221120154624"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"接口和抽象类一样不能被实例化，因为不是类。但是接口可以被实现（使用 implements 关键字）。实现某个接口的类必须在类中实现该接口的全部方法。虽然接口内的方法都是抽象的（和抽象方法很像，没有实现）但是不需要abstract关键字。"}]},{"ID":"20221120154624-km3bzg8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154624-km3bzg8","updated":"20221120154754"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.接口中没有构造方式（因为接口不是类）\n2.接口中的方法必须是抽象的（不能实现）\n3.接口中除了static、final变量，不能有其他变量\n4.接口支持多继承（一个类可以实现多个接口）"}]},{"ID":"20221120154750-xck0s9c","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20221120154750-xck0s9c","updated":"20221120154750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"抽象类和接口的区别："}]},{"ID":"20221120154750-ixhbaia","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20221120154750-ixhbaia","updated":"20221120154801"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.默认的实现方法："}]},{"ID":"20221120154802-sowqhsj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154802-sowqhsj"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（1）抽象类可以有默认的方法实现完全是抽象的。"}]},{"ID":"20221120154750-p6hqihd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154750-p6hqihd","updated":"20221120154750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"抽象类中可以有已经实现了的方法，也可以有被abstract修饰的方法（抽象方法），因为存在抽象方法，所以该类必须是抽象类。"}]},{"ID":"20221120154750-jj5xxg5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154750-jj5xxg5","updated":"20221120154750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（2）接口根本不存在方法的实现。"}]},{"ID":"20221120154750-xdufk5r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154750-xdufk5r","updated":"20221120154750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"但是接口要求只能包含抽象方法，抽象方法是指没有实现的方法。接口就根本不能存在方法的实现。"}]},{"ID":"20221120154750-xml9wyv","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20221120154750-xml9wyv","updated":"20221120154808"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.子类使用的关键词不一样："}]},{"ID":"20221120154808-f3ykik2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154808-f3ykik2"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（1）实现抽象类使用extends关键字来继承抽象类。如果子类不是抽象类的话，它需要提供抽象类中所有声明的方法的实现。"}]},{"ID":"20221120154750-20gzpg1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154750-20gzpg1","updated":"20221120154750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"抽象类虽然不能实例化来使用，但是可以被继承，让子类来具体实现父类的所有抽象方法。但是如果子类将抽象方法没有全部实现，就必须把自己也修饰成抽象类，交于继承它的子类来完成实现。以此类推，直到没有抽象函数。"}]},{"ID":"20221120154750-okgksoo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154750-okgksoo","updated":"20221120154750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（2）子类使用关键字implements来实现接口。它需要提供接口中所有声明的方法的实现。"}]},{"ID":"20221120154750-1eu2pc7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154750-1eu2pc7","updated":"20221120154750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"接口的实现，通过implements关键字。实现该接口的类，必须把接口中的所有方法给实现。不能再推给下一代。（和抽象类相比，抽象类是将梦想传给家族，一代一代去完成。那么接口就是掌门人找大师兄来完成帮派的鸿星伟业，这时候就只有一次希望，要么有能力就实现，没能力就不要接。）"}]},{"ID":"20221120154750-sjhb940","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20221120154750-sjhb940","updated":"20221120154811"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.是否有构造器："}]},{"ID":"20221120154812-aic2ujj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154812-aic2ujj"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（1）抽象类可以有构造器"}]},{"ID":"20221120154750-xh9u5lv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154750-xh9u5lv","updated":"20221120154750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"抽象类是属于类，享有类的所有特性（但是不能实例化），当然包括类的构造方法，也就是构造器。"}]},{"ID":"20221120154750-dupv1jl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154750-dupv1jl","updated":"20221120154750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（2）接口不能有构造器"}]},{"ID":"20221120154750-s1hs0md","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154750-s1hs0md","updated":"20221120154750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"接口是所有抽象方法的集合，注意，是集合，不是类。当然没有构造方法一说，更别提什么构造器了。"}]},{"ID":"20221120154750-ufmx76f","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20221120154750-ufmx76f","updated":"20221120154819"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4.可使用的修饰符："}]},{"ID":"20221120154820-7nidsla","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154820-7nidsla"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（1）抽象方法可以有public、protected和default这些修饰符"}]},{"ID":"20221120154750-pu13rvs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154750-pu13rvs","updated":"20221120154750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"抽象类的目的就是被继承，抽象方法就是为了被重写，所以肯定不能用private修饰符，肯定是可以用public的。但是protected和default也是可以的。"}]},{"ID":"20221120154750-jlnwlh8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154750-jlnwlh8","updated":"20221120154750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（2）接口方法默认修饰符是public。你不可以使用其它修饰符。"}]},{"ID":"20221120154750-rjgrqpz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154750-rjgrqpz","updated":"20221120154750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"接口就有且只有一个public修饰。（感觉抽象类像小儿子各种耍无赖，接口就像私生子，说什么只能是什么）"}]},{"ID":"20221120154750-0ix4ah3","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20221120154750-0ix4ah3","updated":"20221120154824"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5.速度方面："}]},{"ID":"20221120154825-l1uf04s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154825-l1uf04s"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（1）抽象方法比接口速度要快（抽象方法是小儿子，从小吃的好所以跑的快）"}]},{"ID":"20221120154750-dsg7o3w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154750-dsg7o3w","updated":"20221120154750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（2）接口是稍微有点慢的，因为它需要时间去寻找在类中实现的方法。（接口是私生子，从小日子苦，营养不良）"}]},{"ID":"20221120154750-ofmlgaj","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20221120154750-ofmlgaj","updated":"20221120154829"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"6.增加新方法对子类的影响："}]},{"ID":"20221120154830-86quydt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154830-86quydt"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（1）如果你往抽象类中添加新的方法，你可以给它提供默认的实现。因此你不需要改变你现在的代码。"}]},{"ID":"20221120154750-n9f9pn4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154750-n9f9pn4","updated":"20221120154750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"抽象类可以有一些非抽象方法的存在，这些方法被称为默认实现。如果添加一个默认实现方法（不能是抽象方法），就不需要在子类中去实现，所以继承这个抽象类的子类无须改动。"}]},{"ID":"20221120154750-y56tinz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154750-y56tinz","updated":"20221120154750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果你往接口中添加方法，那么你必须改变实现该接口的类。"}]},{"ID":"20221120154750-c6uhr19","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154750-c6uhr19","updated":"20221120154750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（2）接口中只能添加抽象方法，当你添加了抽象方法，实现该接口的类就必须实现这个新添加的方法。"}]},{"ID":"20221120154750-zkwjto3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154750-zkwjto3","updated":"20221120154750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"因为，定义中说的很清楚，接口的实现必须实现所有的方法。所有，当然包括新添加的方法。"}]},{"ID":"20221120154750-snqfkkb","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20221120154750-snqfkkb","updated":"20221120154834"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"7.子类能继承的数量："}]},{"ID":"20221120154834-lkdd0y5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154834-lkdd0y5"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"抽象类在java语言中所表示的是一种继承关系，一个子类只能存在一个父类，但是可以存在多个接口。"}]},{"ID":"20221120154750-kfxjxyh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154750-kfxjxyh","updated":"20221120154750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"java在类的继承上并没有多继承。抽象类属于类，所以可以被继承。但子类只能继承一个父类。"}]},{"ID":"20221120154750-8jmc9km","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154750-8jmc9km","updated":"20221120154750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"java为了实现多继承，使用了接口。一个类可以实现多个接口。继承就好比生了孩子，只能有一个爹，但是这个孩子可以学语文，学数学，学英语等等很多东西，而语文、数学、英语就相当于接口。"}]},{"ID":"20221120154750-bs5rwui","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120154750-bs5rwui","updated":"20221120154839"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"总的来说，因为java中抽象类只有单继承，接口就可以实现多继承。"}]},{"ID":"20220906195126-t2jygcb","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220906195126-t2jygcb","updated":"20220906195126"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"深拷贝浅拷贝？"}]},{"ID":"20220913201003-g50jyu4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220913201003-g50jyu4","updated":"20220913201048"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"深拷贝和浅拷贝都是对象拷贝"}]},{"ID":"20220913202012-wy90j0w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220913202012-wy90j0w","updated":"20220913202012"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"数据分为基本数据类型和引用数据类型。基本数据类型：数据直接存储在栈中；引用数据类型：存储在栈中的是对象的引用地址，真实的对象数据存放在堆内存中。"}]},{"ID":"20220913202032-ignx7od","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220913202032-ignx7od"}},{"ID":"20220913202012-c1xbqjm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220913202012-c1xbqjm","updated":"20220913202019"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"浅拷贝："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对于基本数据类型：直接复制数据值；对于引用数据类型：只是复制了对象的引用地址，新旧对象指向同一个内存地址，修改其中一个对象的值，另一个对象的值也随之改变。"}]},{"ID":"20220913202012-rs3r9zr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220913202012-rs3r9zr","updated":"20220913202021"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"深拷贝："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对于基本数据类型：直接复制数据值；对于引用数据类型：开辟新的内存空间，在新的内存空间里复制一个一模一样的对象，新老对象不共享内存，修改其中一个对象的值，不会影响另一个对象。"}]},{"ID":"20220913202012-wk3yfv8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220913202012-wk3yfv8","updated":"20220913202040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"深拷贝相比于浅拷贝速度较慢并且花销较大。"}]},{"ID":"20220913202041-0kr7yur","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220913202041-0kr7yur"}},{"ID":"20220913201610-ot83ayt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220913201610-ot83ayt","updated":"20220913201807"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"clone是浅拷贝，但是可以通过实现Cloneable接口重写clone方法实现深拷贝，并在clone（）方法中将对象引用的其他对象也要clone一份，这就要求被引用的对象也要实现Cloneable接口，并实现clone（）方法"}]},{"ID":"20220919144720-9pw6vdf","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220919144720-9pw6vdf","updated":"20220919144733"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"静态方法和动态方法的区别"}]},{"ID":"20221008160806-z37dflt","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20221008160806-z37dflt","updated":"20221008160807"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"区别："}]},{"ID":"20220919144735-dbzkwlt","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220919144735-dbzkwlt","updated":"20221008160814"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20221008160753-sjih014","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008160753-sjih014","updated":"20221008160804"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1、静态方法是使用static关键字修饰的方法，属于类的，不属于对象；非静态方法是不使用static关键字修饰的普通方法，属于对象，不属于类。"}]},{"ID":"20221008160812-0ezqa1x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008160812-0ezqa1x"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2、静态方法可以直接调用，类名调用和对象调用；非静态方法只能通过对象调用。"}]},{"ID":"20221008160814-c0k888a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008160814-c0k888a"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3、生命周期不同。"}]}]},{"ID":"20221008160830-kloky5o","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20221008160830-kloky5o","updated":"20221008160830"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"一、静态方法和非静态方法的区别（调用对象、引用变量不同）"}]},{"ID":"20221008160830-tw6hw22","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008160830-tw6hw22","updated":"20221008160830"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"静态方法:是使用static关键字修饰的方法，又叫类方法.属于类的，不属于对象， 在实例化对象之前就可以通过类名.方法名调用静态方法。 （静态属性，静态方法都是属于类的，可以直接通过类名调用）。"}]},{"ID":"20221008160830-s17i23t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008160830-s17i23t","updated":"20221008160830"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A.在静态方法中，可以调用静态方法。"}]},{"ID":"20221008160830-ujhl4yz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008160830-ujhl4yz","updated":"20221008160830"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B.在静态方法中，不能调用非静态方法。"}]},{"ID":"20221008160830-gm4hm10","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008160830-gm4hm10","updated":"20221008160830"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C.在静态方法中，可以引用类变量（即，static修饰的变量）。"}]},{"ID":"20221008160830-n6ux9yh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008160830-n6ux9yh","updated":"20221008160830"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D.在静态方法中，不能引用成员变量（即，没有static修饰的变量）。"}]},{"ID":"20221008160830-ndiq5k4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008160830-ndiq5k4","updated":"20221008160830"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"E.在静态方法中，不能使用super和this关键字"}]},{"ID":"20221008160830-jj7q9rj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008160830-jj7q9rj","updated":"20221008160830"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"非静态方法:是不含有static关键字修饰的普通方法，又称为实例方法，成员方法。属于对象的，不属于类的。（成员属性，成员方法是属于对象的，必须通过new关键字创建对象后，再通过对象调用）。"}]},{"ID":"20221008160830-6mz0s7s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008160830-6mz0s7s","updated":"20221008160830"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A.在普通方法中，可以调用普通方法。"}]},{"ID":"20221008160830-qwx1uol","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008160830-qwx1uol","updated":"20221008160830"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B.在普通方法中，可以调用静态方法"}]},{"ID":"20221008160830-01xrriz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008160830-01xrriz","updated":"20221008160830"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C.在普通方法中，可以引用类变量和成员变量"}]},{"ID":"20221008160830-5b5jy6n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008160830-5b5jy6n","updated":"20221008160830"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D.在普通方法中，可以使用super和this关键字"}]},{"ID":"20221008160830-ouymmid","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20221008160830-ouymmid","updated":"20221008160830"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"二、静态方法和非静态方法的区别（调用方法不同）"}]},{"ID":"20221008160830-ldzs7l6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008160830-ldzs7l6","updated":"20221008160830"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"静态方法可以直接调用，类名调用和对象调用。（类名.方法名 / 对象名.方法名）"}]},{"ID":"20221008160830-s1cccfz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008160830-s1cccfz","updated":"20221008160830"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"但是非静态方法只能通过对象调用。（对象名.方法名）"}]},{"ID":"20221008160830-lt3ks3z","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20221008160830-lt3ks3z","updated":"20221008160830"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"三、静态方法和非静态方法的区别（生命周期不同）"}]},{"ID":"20221008160830-ln7yi2r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008160830-ln7yi2r","updated":"20221008160830"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"静态方法的生命周期跟相应的类一样长，静态方法和静态变量会随着类的定义而被分配和装载入内存中。一直到线程结束，静态属性和方法才会被销毁。（也就是静态方法属于类）"}]},{"ID":"20221008160830-1x2cad8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008160830-1x2cad8","updated":"20221008160830"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"非静态方法的生命周期和类的实例化对象一样长，只有当类实例化了一个对象，非静态方法才会被创建，而当这个对象被销毁时，非静态方法也马上被销毁。（也就是非静态方法属于对象）"}]},{"ID":"20221008160830-j3w45qp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008160830-j3w45qp","updated":"20221008160830"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"总结：类方法可以直接通过类名调用，实例方法必需先实例化类，再初始化对象，然后通过类的实例对象才能调用"}]},{"ID":"20221008160848-13qbnaz","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20221008160848-13qbnaz","updated":"20221008160850"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"举例"}]},{"ID":"20221008160835-nrtbzx3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008160835-nrtbzx3","updated":"20221008160845"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20221008160844-90xkw92.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20221008160912-kbajldr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008160912-kbajldr","updated":"20221008160912"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"静态static变量/方法 在类加载的过程中被初始化，在内存中只存在一份，所以可以把它当作是全局变量/方法。"}]},{"ID":"20220922105358-azsvksq","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220922105358-azsvksq","updated":"20220922105428"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"hashtable、hashmap、treemap关系？"}]},{"ID":"20221008082015-ayfu6wa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008082015-ayfu6wa","updated":"20221008082024"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Properties":{"parent-style":"width: 50%; display: block;","style":"width: 10000px;"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20221008082016-9kiayo6.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"width: 10000px;\" parent-style=\"width: 50%; display: block;\"}"}]},{"ID":"20221008082141-pxn6bk5","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20221008082141-pxn6bk5","updated":"20221008082524"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20221008082142-whmy3tj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008082142-whmy3tj","updated":"20221008082524"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"实现方面"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\nHashMap是继承自AbstractMap类，而HashTable是继承自Dictionary类。它们都同时实现了map、Cloneable（可复制）、Serializable（可序列化）这三个接口。存储的内容是基于key-value的键值对映射，不能有重复的key，而且一个key只能映射一个value。HashSet底层就是基于HashMap实现的。\n"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"为空方面"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\nHashtable的key、value都不能为null；HashMap的key、value可以为null，不过只能有一个key为null，但可以有多个null的value；TreeMap键、值都不能为null。\n"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"排序方面"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\nHashtable、HashMap具有无序特性。TreeMap是利用红黑树实现的（树中的每个节点的值都会大于或等于它的左子树中的所有节点的值，并且小于或等于它的右子树中的所有节点的值），实现了SortMap接口，能够对保存的记录根据键进行排序。所以一般需求排序的情况下首选TreeMap，默认按键的升序排序（深度优先搜索），也可以自定义实现Comparator接口实现排序方式。"}]}]},{"ID":"20221007140539-kqpmles","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221007140539-kqpmles","updated":"20221007140629"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20221007140629-pgpzxjf.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20221008085801-0h6c8cb","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20221008085801-0h6c8cb","updated":"20221008161653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"HashMap数组的长度必须是2的指数次幂"}]},{"ID":"20221008085804-87km3mm","Type":"NodeIFrame","Data":"\u003ciframe src=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/dalianpai/p/14295818.html#:~:text=%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%94%E5%BD%93n%E6%98%AF2%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%82%E6%AC%A1%E6%96%B9%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%9Ahash%20%26%20%28length%20-%201%29,%3D%3D%20hash%20%25%20length%203.%E5%9B%A0%E6%AD%A4%EF%BC%8CHashMap%20%E5%AE%B9%E9%87%8F%E4%B8%BA2%E6%AC%A1%E5%B9%82%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%86%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%9A%84%E7%9A%84%E5%9D%87%E5%8C%80%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%EF%BC%8C%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%91hash%E5%86%B2%E7%AA%81%EF%BC%8C%E6%AF%95%E7%AB%9Fhash%E5%86%B2%E7%AA%81%E8%B6%8A%E5%A4%A7%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E9%93%BE%E7%9A%84%E9%95%BF%E5%BA%A6%E8%B6%8A%E5%A4%A7%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E6%A0%B7%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%9D%E4%BC%9A%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8Ehashmap%E7%9A%84%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD\" data-src=\"\" border=\"0\" frameborder=\"no\" framespacing=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"width: 986px; height: 616px;\"\u003e\u003c/iframe\u003e","Properties":{"id":"20221008085804-87km3mm","updated":"20221008085810"}},{"ID":"20220922105828-bmjn9s0","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220922105828-bmjn9s0","updated":"20220922120151"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"强引用和弱引用"}]},{"ID":"20221007134746-um0rvrr","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20221007134746-um0rvrr","updated":"20221007134746"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"什么是强引用、软引用、弱引用、虚引用？"}]},{"ID":"20221007134746-31khgjb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221007134746-31khgjb","updated":"20221007134755"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"强引用（StrongReference）："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一般指的是对像被new出来，强引用一般不会被jvm收回，但会报OutOfMemory（内存不足）。"}]},{"ID":"20221007135851-mb95e6a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221007135851-mb95e6a","updated":"20221007135851"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对于一个普通的对象，如果没有其他的引用关系，只要超过了引用的作用域或者显式地将相应（强）引用赋值为 null，就是可以被垃圾收集的了"}]},{"ID":"20221007134746-kmgl4l0","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20221007134746-kmgl4l0","updated":"20221007134757"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"Object obj = new Object();\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20221007134812-bta9qp4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221007134812-bta9qp4","updated":"20221007134819"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"软引用（SoftReference）："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"软引用相对来说弱于强引用，当内存足够的时候不会被GC回收，但内存不足时，再试图回收软引用，通过软引用可以做临时缓存。"}]},{"ID":"20221007135726-omi2jxn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221007135726-omi2jxn","updated":"20221007135726"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"应用场景：软引用通常用来实现内存敏感的缓存。如果还有空闲内存，就可以暂时保留缓存，当内存不足时清理掉，这样就保证了使用缓存的同时，不会耗尽内存。"}]},{"ID":"20221007134746-q6qra31","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20221007134746-q6qra31","updated":"20221007134825"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"SoftReferencestring ref = new SoftReferencestring(\"hong\");\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20221007134821-vm7ebri","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221007134821-vm7ebri"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"弱引用（WeakReference）："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"区别于软件引用是生命周期更短，当GC回收启动发现弱引用不管内存满不满，都会被直接回收。"}]},{"ID":"20221007135738-pew20d2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221007135738-pew20d2","updated":"20221007135738"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"应用场景：弱应用同样可用于内存敏感的缓存。"}]},{"ID":"20221007134746-6ftg9q8","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20221007134746-6ftg9q8","updated":"20221007134846"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"Obejct oj = new Object();\nWeakReferenceobejct wf = new WeakReferenceobejct(oj);\noj = null; System.gc(); //下面会发现有时候直接返回null;wf.get();\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20221007134838-ehce087","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221007134838-ehce087","updated":"20221007134908"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"虚引用（PhantomReference）："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这个引用也有人叫幻引用，也很明显，引用一个不存在，随时会被干掉，算是所有引用中最容易被干掉的。"}]},{"ID":"20221007135743-4ba331h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221007135743-4ba331h","updated":"20221007135744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"应用场景：可用来跟踪对象被垃圾回收器回收的活动，当一个虚引用关联的对象被垃圾收集器回收之前会收到一条系统通知"}]},{"ID":"20221007134746-0qegpd7","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20221007134746-0qegpd7","updated":"20221007134910"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"// 虚引用\nObject oj= new Object();\nReferenceQueue req= new ReferenceQueue();\nPhantomReference pr= new PhantomReference(oj, req);\n// 每次返回Null\nSystem.out.println(pr.get());\n//返回是否被删除\nSystem.out.println(pr.isEnqueued());\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20221007135003-tenpd0v","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20221007135003-tenpd0v","updated":"20221007135003"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"总结"}]},{"ID":"20221007135003-ekb0c5g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221007135003-ekb0c5g","updated":"20221007135003"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"    Java4种引用的级别由高到低依次为："}]},{"ID":"20221007135003-sxa3jdb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221007135003-sxa3jdb","updated":"20221007135003"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"强引用  \u0026gt;  软引用  \u0026gt;  弱引用  \u0026gt;  虚引用"}]},{"ID":"20221007135003-r7v75c3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221007135003-r7v75c3","updated":"20221007135003"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"    通过图来看一下他们之间在垃圾回收时的区别："}]},{"ID":"20221007135003-4vl2mth","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221007135003-4vl2mth","updated":"20221007135019"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Properties":{"parent-style":"display: block;"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20221007135016-l73io8j.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: parent-style=\"display: block;\"}"}]},{"ID":"20221007135003-o2wkgr6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221007135003-o2wkgr6","updated":"20221007135003"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"       当垃圾回收器回收时，某些对象会被回收，某些不会被回收。垃圾回收器会从根对象Object来标记存活的对象，然后将某些不可达的对象和一些引用的对象进行回收，如果对这方面不是很了解，可以参考如下的文章："}]},{"ID":"20221007135003-o2all1h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221007135003-o2all1h","updated":"20221007135003"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"      通过表格来说明一下，如下："}]},{"ID":"20221007135003-bpzxp07","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221007135003-bpzxp07","updated":"20221007135029"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Properties":{"parent-style":"display: block;"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20221007135025-qxpuy70.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: parent-style=\"display: block;\"}"}]},{"ID":"20221007134746-yez98yq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221007134746-yez98yq","updated":"20221008090708"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不管哪种引用，在开发过程中，都是尽量减少强引用，毕竟内存有限，虽然说放到内存可以提升用户访问效率，但是这也是一把双刃剑，有利上定有弊，过于依赖内存，就会导致不足和溢出后面就jj了..."}]},{"ID":"20220922144650-7lastqi","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220922144650-7lastqi","updated":"20220922185838"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"stringbuffer和stringbuilder"}]},{"ID":"20220922190418-v9uw5ym","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220922190418-v9uw5ym","updated":"20220922193104"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"treemap和hashmap是否有序，是按什么规则排序的"}]},{"ID":"20221008161442-fo28wgx","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20221008161442-fo28wgx","updated":"20221008161450"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"什么时候用treemap和hashmap"}]},{"ID":"20221008161526-t6rira8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008161526-t6rira8","updated":"20221008161526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对于在Map中插入、删除和定位元素这类操作，HashMap是 好的选择。"}]},{"ID":"20221008161533-fci0aym","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008161533-fci0aym"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"然而，假如你需要对一个有序的key集合进行遍历，TreeMap是更好的选择。"}]},{"ID":"20221008161535-d7rqe85","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008161535-d7rqe85"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"基于你的collection的大小，也许向HashMap中添加元素会更快，将map换为TreeMap进行有序key的遍历"}]},{"ID":"20220923083035-v8hybrx","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220923083035-v8hybrx","updated":"20220923083044"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一般捕获什么异常"}]},{"ID":"20221027121426-49byd6p","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20221027121426-49byd6p","updated":"20221027121814"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20221027121427-9pcgcdn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221027121427-9pcgcdn","updated":"20221027121814"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"比如项目中的用户名重复错误，可以设置一个全局异常的类，用@ControllerAdvice注解指定包含哪些注解的类需要进行捕获异常，然后用@ExceptionHandler指定SQL相关的异常，最后在开发的时候将遇到的异常问题通过关键字分别进行捕获抛异常"}]}]},{"ID":"20221120152507-31kqtl1","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20221120152507-31kqtl1","updated":"20221120152519"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"error和exception的区别"}]},{"ID":"20221008133400-2xqm6fb","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20221008133400-2xqm6fb","updated":"20221008133417"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"@Before@After@Test"}]},{"ID":"20221008133418-rcauaeq","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20221008133418-rcauaeq","updated":"20221008133422"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20221008133421-nnmals3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008133421-nnmals3","updated":"20221008133422"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"@Before 和 @After 是junit工具包中的类，@Before在执行@Test 测试其主要业务之前加载，@After 在执行@Test 测试完成之后加载。"}]}]},{"ID":"20220922105543-utf3ahr","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220922105543-utf3ahr","updated":"20220922144806"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"接口如何进行测试的？"}]},{"ID":"20220922105727-g5to22s","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220922105727-g5to22s","updated":"20220922144818"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"输入体（json）是什么样的？cookie"}]},{"ID":"20220922105808-s56y87v","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220922105808-s56y87v","updated":"20220922105906"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"双向链表最后叶子节点指向哪？"}]},{"ID":"20220922120153-rmbidja","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220922120153-rmbidja","updated":"20220922144648"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"日志如何整合保存"}]},{"ID":"20221008101940-tkl6o37","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20221008101940-tkl6o37","updated":"20221008132654"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"this作用"}]},{"ID":"20221028094924-uys0ntq","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20221028094924-uys0ntq","updated":"20221028095007"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"什么是内存溢出和内存泄露？"}]},{"ID":"20221028094926-lfr6n0s","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20221028094926-lfr6n0s","updated":"20221028094959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20221028094943-kiz3t7k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221028094943-kiz3t7k","updated":"20221028094959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"溢出是指创建太多对象导致内存空间不足，泄漏是无用对象没有回收"}]}]},{"ID":"20221027143955-wlg5ly5","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20221027143955-wlg5ly5","updated":"20221027144000"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"重写和重载的区别"}]},{"ID":"20221027144002-xu5d34h","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20221027144002-xu5d34h","updated":"20221027144057"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.重写(Override)"}]},{"ID":"20221027144058-9ehtzeg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221027144058-9ehtzeg"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"从字面上看，重写就是 重新写一遍的意思。其实就是在子类中把父类本身有的方法重新写一遍。子类继承了父类原有的方法，但有时子类并不想原封不动的继承父类中的某个方法，所以在方法名，参数列表，返回类型(除过子类中方法的返回值是父类中方法返回值的子类时)都相同的情况下， 对方法体进行修改或重写，这就是重写。但要注意子类函数的访问修饰权限不能少于父类的。\n例如："}]},{"ID":"20221027144043-x5eeaec","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20221027144043-x5eeaec","updated":"20221027144211"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"public class Father {\n\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        // TODO Auto-generated method stub\n        Son s = new Son();\n        s.sayHello();\n    }\n\n    public void sayHello() {\n        System.out.println(\"Hello\");\n    }\n}\n\nclass Son extends Father{\n\n    @Override\n    public void sayHello() {\n        // TODO Auto-generated method stub\n        System.out.println(\"hello by \");\n    }\n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20221027144036-rj0f8wm","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20221027144036-rj0f8wm","updated":"20221027144106"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"重写 总结："}]},{"ID":"20221027144107-52q6qyd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221027144107-52q6qyd"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.发生在父类与子类之间\n2.方法名，参数列表，返回类型（除过子类中方法的返回类型是父类中返回类型的子类）必须相同\n3.访问修饰符的限制一定要大于被重写方法的访问修饰符（public\u003eprotected\u003edefault\u003eprivate)\n4.重写方法一定不能抛出新的检查异常或者比被重写方法申明更加宽泛的检查型异常"}]},{"ID":"20221027144002-3o80f1u","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20221027144002-3o80f1u","updated":"20221027144115"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.重载(Overload)"}]},{"ID":"20221027144116-qceptfb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221027144116-qceptfb"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在一个类中，同名的方法如果有不同的参数列表（参数类型不同、参数个数不同甚至是参数顺序不同）则视为重载。同时，重载对返回类型没有要求，可以相同也可以不同，但不能通过返回类型是否相同来判断重载。\n例如："}]},{"ID":"20221027144134-f1smpfn","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20221027144134-f1smpfn","updated":"20221027144142"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"public class Father {\n\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        // TODO Auto-generated method stub\n        Father s = new Father();\n        s.sayHello();\n        s.sayHello(\"wintershii\");\n\n    }\n\n    public void sayHello() {\n        System.out.println(\"Hello\");\n    }\n\n    public void sayHello(String name) {\n        System.out.println(\"Hello\" + \" \" + name);\n    }\n}\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20221027144128-97o0ct9","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20221027144128-97o0ct9","updated":"20221027144154"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"重载 总结："}]},{"ID":"20221027144154-9hdokzw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221027144154-9hdokzw"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.重载Overload是一个类中多态性的一种表现\n2.重载要求同名方法的参数列表不同(参数类型，参数个数甚至是参数顺序)\n3.重载的时候，返回值类型可以相同也可以不相同。无法以返回型别作为重载函数的区分标准"}]},{"ID":"20221027144002-me0lwv5","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20221027144002-me0lwv5","updated":"20221027144159"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"面试时，问：重载（Overload）和重写（Override）的区别？"}]},{"ID":"20221027144159-yb0stst","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221027144159-yb0stst","updated":"20221027151039"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答：方法的重载和重写都是实现多态的方式，区别在于前者实现的是编译时的多态性，而后者实现的是运行时的多态性。重载发生在一个类中，同名的方法如果有不同的参数列表（参数类型不同、参数个数不同或者二者都不同）则视为重载；重写发生在子类与父类之间，重写要求子类被重写方法与父类被重写方法有相同的参数列表，有兼容的返回类型，比父类被重写方法更好访问，不能比父类被重写方法声明更多的异常（里氏代换原则）。重载对返回类型没有特殊的要求，不能根据返回类型进行区分。"}]},{"ID":"20221027151028-hagv5eg","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20221027151028-hagv5eg","updated":"20221027151036"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"项目遇到什么困难"}]},{"ID":"20221010145919-mffjy9y","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20221010145919-mffjy9y","updated":"20221010145926"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"多线程"}]},{"ID":"20221117202250-24xqanj","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20221117202250-24xqanj","updated":"20221117202257"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"线程和进程的区别"}]},{"ID":"20221120160712-xu2841v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120160712-xu2841v","updated":"20221120160724"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"根本区别："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"进程是操作系统资源分配的基本单位，而线程是处理器任务调度和执行的基本单位"}]},{"ID":"20221120160712-z31bp2p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120160712-z31bp2p","updated":"20221120160725"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"资源开销"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"每个进程都有独立的代码和数据空间（程序上下文），程序之间的切换会有较大的开销；线程可以看做轻量级的进程，同一类线程共享代码和数据空间，每个线程都有自己独立的运行栈和程序计数器（PC），线程之间切换的开销小。"}]},{"ID":"20221120160712-0yji6pl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120160712-0yji6pl","updated":"20221120160721"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"包含关系："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果一个进程内有多个线程，则执行过程不是一条线的，而是多条线（线程）共同完成的；线程是进程的一部分，所以线程也被称为轻权进程或者轻量级进程。"}]},{"ID":"20221120160712-s01l3ne","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120160712-s01l3ne","updated":"20221120160720"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"内存分配："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"同一进程的线程共享本进程的地址空间和资源，而进程之间的地址空间和资源是相互独立的"}]},{"ID":"20221120160712-yftc4ko","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120160712-yftc4ko","updated":"20221120160718"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"影响关系："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一个进程崩溃后，在保护模式下不会对其他进程产生影响，但是一个线程崩溃整个进程都死掉。所以多进程要比多线程健壮。"}]},{"ID":"20221120160712-w88zzlo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120160712-w88zzlo","updated":"20221120161551"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"执行过程："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"每个独立的进程有程序运行的入口、顺序执行序列和程序出口。但是线程不能独立执行，必须依存在应用程序中，由应用程序提供多个线程执行控制，两者均可并发执行"}]},{"ID":"20220906195126-ac5d2gk","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220906195126-ac5d2gk","updated":"20220906195126"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"互斥锁"}]},{"ID":"20220906195126-p14ewz4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906195126-p14ewz4","updated":"20220906195228"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20220906195220-2amnrt7.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20220906195228-0wex6tb.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20220907094723-7f2ah70","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220907094723-7f2ah70","updated":"20220907094730"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"死锁"}]},{"ID":"20220907094925-19kapwx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220907094925-19kapwx","updated":"20220907094926"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20220907094926-icpv8q2.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20220907094731-8yelh9a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220907094731-8yelh9a","updated":"20220907094944"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20220907094944-qaczvq6.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20220907095233-5g6r04d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220907095233-5g6r04d","updated":"20220907095233"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20220907095233-digr98u.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20220907095248-5ye51xy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220907095248-5ye51xy","updated":"20220907095248"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20220907095248-ciot3k1.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20220919154332-oz3rar7","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220919154332-oz3rar7","updated":"20220919163734"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"线程的五个状态"}]},{"ID":"20220919163735-efuhx86","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220919163735-efuhx86","updated":"20220919163744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20220919163744-14auha9.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20221008142109-twrj5c9","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20221008142109-twrj5c9","updated":"20221008161620"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"多线程实现的四种方式"}]},{"ID":"20221008142752-k475qtn","Type":"NodeIFrame","Data":"\u003ciframe src=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/ericz2j/p/10281572.html#:~:text=Java%E5%A4%9A%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%9B%E7%A7%8D%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%201%201.Java%E5%A4%9A%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E6%9C%89%E5%9B%9B%E7%A7%8D%EF%BC%9A%201.%E7%BB%A7%E6%89%BFThread%E7%B1%BB%EF%BC%8C%E9%87%8D%E5%86%99run%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%202.%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0Runnable%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3%EF%BC%8C%E9%87%8D%E5%86%99run%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0Runnable%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E7%B1%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E4%BE%8B%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BAThread%E6%9E%84%E9%80%A0%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E7%9A%84target%203.%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87Callable%E5%92%8CFutureTask%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B%204.%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B%E6%B1%A0%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B,2%202.Thread%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%20%E7%BB%A7%E6%89%BFThread%E7%B1%BB%EF%BC%8C%E9%87%8D%E5%86%99run%20%28%29%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BAThread%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8start%20%28%29%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B%E3%80%82%20...%203%203.Runnable%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F\" data-src=\"\" border=\"0\" frameborder=\"no\" framespacing=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"width: 1289px; height: 717px;\"\u003e\u003c/iframe\u003e","Properties":{"id":"20221008142752-k475qtn","updated":"20221008142753"}},{"ID":"20220922104629-uubg7yg","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220922104629-uubg7yg","updated":"20220922104655"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"join和wait的区别？"}]},{"ID":"20221008140708-tsax3c0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008140708-tsax3c0","updated":"20221008140708"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"java中的wait()方法"}]},{"ID":"20221008140708-kbn9gs0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008140708-kbn9gs0","updated":"20221008140708"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"wait()方法的作用是让当前线程进入等待状态，wait()会与notify()和notifyAll()方法一起使用。"}]},{"ID":"20221008140708-7x6rwk5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008140708-7x6rwk5","updated":"20221008140708"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"notify()和notifyAll()方法的作用是唤醒等待中的线程，notify()方法：唤醒单个线程，notifyAll()方法：唤醒所有线程。"}]},{"ID":"20221008140708-xmdmgfs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008140708-xmdmgfs","updated":"20221008140708"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"java中的join()方法"}]},{"ID":"20221008140708-ytx0530","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008140708-ytx0530","updated":"20221008140708"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"join()方法是等待这个线程结束，完成其执行。它的主要起同步作用，使线程之间的执行从“并行”变成“串行”。"}]},{"ID":"20221008140708-ef0evxd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008140708-ef0evxd","updated":"20221008140708"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"也就是说，当我们在线程A中调用了线程B的join()方法时，线程执行过程发生改变：线程A，必须等待线程B执行完毕后，才可以继续执行下去。"}]},{"ID":"20221008140708-h32o5gp","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20221008140708-h32o5gp","updated":"20221008140708"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"wait()方法和join()方法的相似处"}]},{"ID":"20221008140708-t1xkj02","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008140708-t1xkj02","updated":"20221008140708"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1、wait()和join()方法都用于暂停Java中的当前线程，进入等待状态。"}]},{"ID":"20221008140708-fx457ts","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008140708-fx457ts","updated":"20221008140708"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2、在Java中都可以调用interrupt()方法中断wait()和join()的线程状态。"}]},{"ID":"20221008140708-m9u9pty","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008140708-m9u9pty","updated":"20221008140708"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3、wait()和join()都是非静态方法。"}]},{"ID":"20221008140708-qkrhhw2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008140708-qkrhhw2","updated":"20221008140708"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4、wait()和join()都在Java中重载。wait()和join（）没有超时，但接受超时参数。"}]},{"ID":"20221008140708-d6hagf9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008140708-d6hagf9","updated":"20221008140708"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尽管wait()方法和join()方法有相似之处，但wait()方法和join()方法还是存在差异的。"}]},{"ID":"20221008140708-m4cz8ib","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20221008140708-m4cz8ib","updated":"20221008140708"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"wait()方法和join()方法之间的区别"}]},{"ID":"20221008140717-jeesrgb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008140717-jeesrgb","updated":"20221008140717"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"1、存在不同的java包中"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" （最明显的区别）"}]},{"ID":"20221008140717-c3pamdg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008140717-c3pamdg","updated":"20221008140717"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"wait()方法需要在java.lang.Object类中声明；而，join()方法是在java.lang.Thread类中声明。"}]},{"ID":"20221008140717-26jb2da","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008140717-26jb2da","updated":"20221008140717"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"2、使用目的不同"}]},{"ID":"20221008140717-k0f21um","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008140717-k0f21um","updated":"20221008140717"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"wait()方法用于线程间通信；而join()方法用于在多个线程之间添加排序，第二个线程需要在第一个线程执行完成后才能开始执行。"}]},{"ID":"20221008140717-5ny2yil","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008140717-5ny2yil","updated":"20221008140717"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"3、唤醒线程方面的区别"}]},{"ID":"20221008140717-yc1ctne","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008140717-yc1ctne","updated":"20221008140717"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们可以通过使用notify()和notifyAll()方法启动一个通过wait()方法进入等待状态的线程。但是我们不能打破join()方法所施加的等待，除非或者中断调用了连接的线程已执行完了。"}]},{"ID":"20221008140717-7ncnunt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008140717-7ncnunt","updated":"20221008140717"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"4、同步上下文"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" （最重要的区别）"}]},{"ID":"20221008140717-3riudjt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008140717-3riudjt","updated":"20221008140717"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"wait()方法必须从同步（synchronized）的上下文调用，即同步块或方法，否则会抛出IllegalMonitorStateException异常。"}]},{"ID":"20221008140717-egbl40a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008140717-egbl40a","updated":"20221008140717"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"但，在Java中有或没有同步的上下文，我们都可以调用join()方法。"}]},{"ID":"20220921100128-pr4bgmj","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220921100128-pr4bgmj","updated":"20220922091955"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"线程同步和互斥的区别"}]},{"ID":"20220922091956-8i9gtxh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220922091956-8i9gtxh","updated":"20220922091956"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20220922091956-fdr6xmi.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20220922105249-ucof7k5","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220922105249-ucof7k5","updated":"20221007140145"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"concurrenthashmap是否线程安全"}]},{"ID":"20221007140423-2hdxke5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221007140423-2hdxke5","updated":"20221007140425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"安全"}]},{"ID":"20221010151021-bzvttml","Type":"NodeIFrame","Data":"\u003ciframe src=\"https://xueyici.com/archives/7071817389322534942\" data-src=\"\" border=\"0\" frameborder=\"no\" framespacing=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"width: 888px; height: 534px;\"\u003e\u003c/iframe\u003e","Properties":{"id":"20221010151021-bzvttml","updated":"20221010151021"}},{"ID":"20221008141221-iy3pd6u","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20221008141221-iy3pd6u","updated":"20221008141226"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"线程之间的通信"}]},{"ID":"20221008155446-zo31p7b","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20221008155446-zo31p7b","updated":"20221008155446"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"进程通信"}]},{"ID":"20221008155446-2wjbbjk","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20221008155446-2wjbbjk","updated":"20221008155446"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"管道(pipe)"}]},{"ID":"20221008155446-q3ekn0j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008155446-q3ekn0j","updated":"20221008155446"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"管道是一种半双工的通信方式，数据只能单向流动，而且只能在具有亲缘关系的进程间使用。进程的亲缘关系通常是指父子进程关系。"}]},{"ID":"20221008155446-8uax6d9","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20221008155446-8uax6d9","updated":"20221008155446"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有名管道 (namedpipe)"}]},{"ID":"20221008155446-zb62vb5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008155446-zb62vb5","updated":"20221008155446"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有名管道也是半双工的通信方式，但是它允许无亲缘关系进程间的通信。"}]},{"ID":"20221008155446-qj2hkvx","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20221008155446-qj2hkvx","updated":"20221008155446"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"信号量(semaphore)"}]},{"ID":"20221008155446-wyt5ndg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008155446-wyt5ndg","updated":"20221008155446"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"信号量是一个计数器，可以用来控制多个进程对共享资源的访问。它常作为一种锁机制，防止某进程正在访问共享资源时，其他进程也访问该资源。因此，主要作为进程间以及同一进程内不同线程之间的同步手段。"}]},{"ID":"20221008155446-5dyov5o","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20221008155446-5dyov5o","updated":"20221008155446"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"消息队列(messagequeue)"}]},{"ID":"20221008155446-24cmdi2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008155446-24cmdi2","updated":"20221008155446"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"消息队列是由消息的链表，存放在内核中并由消息队列标识符标识。消息队列克服了信号传递信息少、管道只能承载无格式字节流以及缓冲区大小受限等缺点。"}]},{"ID":"20221008155446-tbg9ng7","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20221008155446-tbg9ng7","updated":"20221008155446"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"信号 (sinal)"}]},{"ID":"20221008155446-v8ighqs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008155446-v8ighqs","updated":"20221008155446"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"信号是一种比较复杂的通信方式，用于通知接收进程某个事件已经发生。"}]},{"ID":"20221008155446-oo4p6gw","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20221008155446-oo4p6gw","updated":"20221008155446"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"共享内存(shared memory)"}]},{"ID":"20221008155446-0ns7t1y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008155446-0ns7t1y","updated":"20221008155446"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"共享内存就是映射一段能被其他进程所访问的内存，这段共享内存由一个进程创建，但多个进程都可以访问。共享内存是最快的 IPC 方式，它是针对其他进程间通信方式运行效率低而专门设计的。它往往与其他通信机制，如信号量，配合使用，来实现进程间的同步和通信。"}]},{"ID":"20221008155446-475b3vc","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20221008155446-475b3vc","updated":"20221008155446"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"套接字(socket)"}]},{"ID":"20221008155446-2q5yx7o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008155446-2q5yx7o","updated":"20221008155446"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"套接口也是一种进程间通信机制，与其他通信机制不同的是，它可用于不同设备及其间的进程通信。"}]},{"ID":"20221008155511-fbnnagp","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20221008155511-fbnnagp","updated":"20221008155511"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"线程间的通信方式"}]},{"ID":"20221008155511-hu8xye9","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20221008155511-hu8xye9","updated":"20221008155511"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"锁机制：包括互斥锁、条件变量、读写锁"}]},{"ID":"20221008155511-amxgvz8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008155511-amxgvz8","updated":"20221008155511"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"互斥锁提供了以排他方式防止数据结构被并发修改的方法。\n读写锁允许多个线程同时读共享数据，而对写操作是互斥的。\n条件变量可以以原子的方式阻塞进程，直到某个特定条件为真为止。对条件的测试是在互斥锁的保护下进行的。条件变量始终与互斥锁一起使用。"}]},{"ID":"20221008155511-p97epgc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008155511-p97epgc","updated":"20221008155511"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"wait/notify 等待"}]},{"ID":"20221008155511-rv58277","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008155511-rv58277","updated":"20221008155511"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Volatile 内存共享"}]},{"ID":"20221008155511-sc53v4y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008155511-sc53v4y","updated":"20221008155511"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"CountDownLatch 并发工具"}]},{"ID":"20221008155511-rewx7sq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008155511-rewx7sq","updated":"20221008155511"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"CyclicBarrier 并发工具"}]},{"ID":"20221008155511-h73pt8n","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20221008155511-h73pt8n","updated":"20221008155511"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"信号量机制(Semaphore)"}]},{"ID":"20221008155511-f91jllu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008155511-f91jllu","updated":"20221008155511"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"包括无名线程信号量和命名线程信号量。"}]},{"ID":"20221008155511-hyc14sn","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20221008155511-hyc14sn","updated":"20221008155511"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"信号机制(Signal)"}]},{"ID":"20221008155511-uh2ctuj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008155511-uh2ctuj","updated":"20221008155511"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"类似进程间的信号处理。"}]},{"ID":"20221008155511-rzhdgad","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008155511-rzhdgad","updated":"20221008155511"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"线程间的通信目的主要是用于线程同步，所以线程没有像进程通信中的用于数据交换的通信机制。"}]},{"ID":"20221008082805-ct4s9bj","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20221008082805-ct4s9bj","updated":"20221008082807"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"虚拟线程"}]},{"ID":"20221008140457-4aiy5sj","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20221008140457-4aiy5sj","updated":"20221008140501"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"线程池"}]},{"ID":"20221120141627-ns6roi9","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20221120141627-ns6roi9","updated":"20221120141639"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"volatile特点"}]},{"ID":"20221120143752-p68hmuw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120143752-p68hmuw","updated":"20221120143755"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20221120143755-6bo4cdo.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20221120143804-ismitm3","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20221120143804-ismitm3","updated":"20221120143804"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Volatile关键字的作用："}]},{"ID":"20221120143804-wu0upcn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120143804-wu0upcn","updated":"20221120143857"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"  \t"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color8);"},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"其实volatile关键字的作用就是保证了可见性和有序性（不保证原子性），如果一个共享变量被volatile关键字修饰，那么如果一个线程修改了这个共享变量后，其他线程是立马可知的。如果线程A修改了自己的共享变量副本，这时如果该共享变量没有被volatile修饰，那么本次修改不一定会马上将修改结果刷新到主存中，如果此时B去主存中读取共享变量的值，那么这个值就是没有被A修改之前的值。如果该共享变量被volatile修饰了，那么本次修改结果会强制立刻刷新到主存中，如果此时B去主存中读取共享变量的值，那么这个值就是被A修改之后的值了。"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color8);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\n　　volatile禁止指令重排序优化，在指令重排序优化时，在volatile变量之前的指令不能在volatile之后执行，在volatile之后的指令也不能在volatile之前执行，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color8);"},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"所以它保证了有序性"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color8);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。\n　　volatile 的读性能消耗与普通变量几乎相同，但是"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color8);"},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"写操作稍慢"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color8);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，因为它需要在本地代码中插入许多内存屏障指令（是一种CPU指令，用于控制特定条件下的重排序和内存可见性问题。Java编译器也会根据内存屏障的规则禁止重排序。）来保证处理器不发生乱序执行。"}]},{"ID":"20221120143759-5ixl0ft","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120143759-5ixl0ft"}},{"ID":"20221120141915-x33drad","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120141915-x33drad","updated":"20221120141915"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\tJava语言提供了一种稍弱的同步机制，即volatile变量，用来确保将变量的更新操作通知到其他线程。当把变量声明为volatile类型后，编译器与运行时都会注意到这个变量是共享的，因此不会将该变量上的操作与其他内存操作一起重排序。volatile变量不会被缓存在寄存器或者对其他处理器不可见的地方，因此在读取volatile类型的变量时总会返回最新写入的值。"}]},{"ID":"20221120141915-avp5u0f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120141915-avp5u0f","updated":"20221120141915"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"　　在访问volatile变量时不会执行加锁操作，因此也就不会使执行线程阻塞，因此volatile变量是一种比sychronized关键字更轻量级的同步机制。"}]},{"ID":"20221120141922-ea147wy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120141922-ea147wy","updated":"20221120141923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20221120141923-q515t19.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20221120141915-5q3ztqm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120141915-5q3ztqm","updated":"20221120141915"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"　　当对非 volatile 变量进行读写的时候，每个线程先从内存拷贝变量到CPU缓存中。如果计算机有多个CPU，每个线程可能在不同的CPU上被处理，这意味着每个线程可以拷贝到不同的 CPU cache 中。"}]},{"ID":"20221120141915-d1lthyk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120141915-d1lthyk","updated":"20221120141915"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"　　而声明变量是 volatile 的，JVM 保证了每次读变量都从内存中读，跳过 CPU cache 这一"}]},{"ID":"20221120141813-ogv0jgb","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20221120141813-ogv0jgb","updated":"20221120141813"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当一个变量定义为 volatile 之后，将具备两种特性："}]},{"ID":"20221120141813-3t1w2wg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120141813-3t1w2wg","updated":"20221120141813"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"　　1.保证此变量对所有的线程的可见性，这里的“可见性”，如本文开头所述，当一个线程修改了这个变量的值，volatile 保证了新值能立即同步到主内存，以及每次使用前立即从主内存刷新。但普通变量做不到这点，普通变量的值在线程间传递均需要通过主内存（详见："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"http://www.cnblogs.com/zhengbin/p/6407137.html","TextMarkTextContent":"Java内存模型"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"）来完成。"}]},{"ID":"20221120141813-jhaqny1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120141813-jhaqny1","updated":"20221120141813"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"　　2.禁止指令重排序优化。有volatile修饰的变量，赋值后多执行了一个“load addl $0x0, (%esp)”操作，这个操作相当于一个 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"内存屏障"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" （指令重排序时不能把后面的指令重排序到内存屏障之前的位置），只有一个CPU访问内存时，并不需要内存屏障；（什么是指令重排序：是指CPU采用了允许将多条指令不按程序规定的顺序分开发送给各相应电路单元处理）。"}]},{"ID":"20221120141813-5jsn00h","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20221120141813-5jsn00h","updated":"20221120141813"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"volatile 性能："}]},{"ID":"20221120141813-x54d473","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120141813-x54d473","updated":"20221120141813"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"　　volatile 的读性能消耗与普通变量几乎相同，但是写操作稍慢，因为它需要在本地代码中插入许多内存屏障指令来保证处理器不发生乱序执行。"}]},{"ID":"20221120144014-zz48yow","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20221120144014-zz48yow","updated":"20221120151308"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Volatile和synchronized的区别 ：　　"}]},{"ID":"20221120144021-ntftnjm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120144021-ntftnjm","updated":"20221120144031"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（1）volatile只能作用于变量，使用范围较小。synchronized可以用在变量、方法、类、同步代码块等，使用范围比较广。\n（2）volatile只能保证可见性和有序性，不能保证原子性。而可见性、有序性、原子性synchronized都可以包证。\n（3）volatile不会造成线程阻塞。synchronized可能会造成线程阻塞。\n（4）在性能方面synchronized关键字是防止多个线程同时执行一段代码，就会影响程序执行效率，而volatile关键字在某些情况下性能要优于synchronized。"}]},{"ID":"20221120144131-7vp2cev","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20221120144131-7vp2cev","updated":"20221120151317"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"什么是重排序 ："}]},{"ID":"20221120144137-kmp9q94","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120144137-kmp9q94"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"重排序是指编译器和处理器为了优化程序性能而对指令序列进行重新排序的一种手段。但是重排序可以保证最终执行的结果是与程序顺序执行的结果一致，并且只会对不存在数据依赖性的指令进行重排序，这个重排序在单线程下对最终执行结果是没有影响的，但是在多线程下就会存在问题。"}]},{"ID":"20221120144132-mrqfytd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221120144132-mrqfytd","updated":"20221120144146"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20221120144146-a665ulw.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20221010145927-jlnnc8a","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20221010145927-jlnnc8a","updated":"20221010145933"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"MySQL"}]},{"ID":"20220906195126-s0apt7h","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220906195126-s0apt7h","updated":"20220906195126"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"三大范式？"}]},{"ID":"20220921094423-l69x7yd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220921094423-l69x7yd","updated":"20220921094423"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"1"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"．第一范式(确保每列保持原子性)"}]},{"ID":"20220921094423-dg7fd71","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220921094423-dg7fd71","updated":"20220921094423"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第一范式是最基本的范式。如果数据库表中的所有字段值都是不可分解的原子值，就说明该数据库表满足了第一范式。"}]},{"ID":"20220921094423-gchc5gc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220921094423-gchc5gc","updated":"20220921094423"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第一范式的合理遵循需要根据系统的实际需求来定。比如某些数据库系统中需要用到“地址”这个属性，本来直接将“地址”属性设计成一个数据库表的字段就行。但是如果系统经常会访问“地址”属性中的“城市”部分，那么就非要将“地址”这个属性重新拆分为省份、城市、详细地址等多个部分进行存储，这样在对地址中某一部分操作的时候将非常方便。这样设计才算满足了数据库的第一范式，如下表所示。"}]},{"ID":"20220921094423-nk3fus2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220921094423-nk3fus2","updated":"20220921094543"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20220921094543-mpq2lms.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20220921094423-teb8tv2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220921094423-teb8tv2","updated":"20220921094423"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"上表所示的用户信息遵循了第一范式的要求，这样在对用户使用城市进行分类的时候就非常方便，也提高了数据库的性能。"}]},{"ID":"20220921094423-dupc6kt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220921094423-dupc6kt","updated":"20220921094423"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"2"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"．第二范式(确保表中的每列都和主键相关)"}]},{"ID":"20220921094423-6fewib0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220921094423-6fewib0","updated":"20220921094423"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第二范式在第一范式的基础之上更进一层。第二范式需要确保数据库表中的每一列都和主键相关，而不能只与主键的某一部分相关（主要针对联合主键而言）。也就是说在一个数据库表中，一个表中只能保存一种数据，不可以把多种数据保存在同一张数据库表中。"}]},{"ID":"20220921094423-oor4yyi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220921094423-oor4yyi","updated":"20220921094423"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"比如要设计一个订单信息表，因为订单中可能会有多种商品，所以要将订单编号和商品编号作为数据库表的联合主键，如下表所示。"}]},{"ID":"20220921094423-brcriwj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220921094423-brcriwj","updated":"20220921094423"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"订单信息表"}]},{"ID":"20220921094423-zvxh5o1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220921094423-zvxh5o1","updated":"20220921094556"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20220921094556-h3a8hc4.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20220921094423-94ib0mb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220921094423-94ib0mb","updated":"20220921094423"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这样就产生一个问题：这个表中是以订单编号和商品编号作为联合主键。这样在该表中商品名称、单位、商品价格等信息不与该表的主键相关，而仅仅是与商品编号相关。所以在这里违反了第二范式的设计原则。"}]},{"ID":"20220921094423-sulipkf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220921094423-sulipkf","updated":"20220921094423"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"而如果把这个订单信息表进行拆分，把商品信息分离到另一个表中，把订单项目表也分离到另一个表中，就非常完美了。如下所示。"}]},{"ID":"20220921094423-qrfvob2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220921094423-qrfvob2","updated":"20220921094606"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20220921094605-zerbrim.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20220921094423-hlo23w8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220921094423-hlo23w8","updated":"20220921094423"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这样设计，在很大程度上减小了数据库的冗余。如果要获取订单的商品信息，使用商品编号到商品信息表中查询即可。"}]},{"ID":"20220921094423-qscohqd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220921094423-qscohqd","updated":"20220921094423"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"3"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"．第三范式(确保每列都和主键列直接相关,而不是间接相关)"}]},{"ID":"20220921094423-vzrk9g2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220921094423-vzrk9g2","updated":"20220921094423"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第三范式需要确保数据表中的每一列数据都和主键直接相关，而不能间接相关。"}]},{"ID":"20220921094423-my9u72m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220921094423-my9u72m","updated":"20220921094423"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"比如在设计一个订单数据表的时候，可以将客户编号作为一个外键和订单表建立相应的关系。而不可以在订单表中添加关于客户其它信息（比如姓名、所属公司等）的字段。如下面这两个表所示的设计就是一个满足第三范式的数据库表。"}]},{"ID":"20220921094423-ys6kt6a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220921094423-ys6kt6a","updated":"20220921094611"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20220921094611-namks8u.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20220921094423-7vfl1vg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220921094423-7vfl1vg","updated":"20220921094423"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这样在查询订单信息的时候，就可以使用客户编号来引用客户信息表中的记录，也不必在订单信息表中多次输入客户信息的内容，减小了数据冗余。"}]},{"ID":"20220921094423-d9ebd1d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220921094423-d9ebd1d","updated":"20220921094423"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"注意事项："}]},{"ID":"20220921094423-op54xic","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220921094423-op54xic","updated":"20220921094423"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.第二范式与第三范式的本质区别：在于有没有分出两张表。"}]},{"ID":"20220921094423-i6jlr98","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220921094423-i6jlr98","updated":"20220921094423"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第二范式是说一张表中包含了多种不同实体的属性，那么必须要分成多张表，第三范式是要求已经分好了多张表的话，一张表中只能有另一张标的ID，而不能有其他任何信息，（其他任何信息，一律用主键在另一张表中查询）。"}]},{"ID":"20220921094423-z0wj75d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220921094423-z0wj75d","updated":"20220921094423"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.必须先满足第一范式才能满足第二范式，必须同时满足第一第二范式才能满足第三范式。"}]},{"ID":"20220906195126-q28pvw2","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220906195126-q28pvw2","updated":"20220906195126"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"给场景如何设计表？"}]},{"ID":"20220906195126-obofpyp","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220906195126-obofpyp","updated":"20220906195126"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"权限怎么设计？"}]},{"ID":"20220919212145-njczk2z","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220919212145-njczk2z","updated":"20220919212148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"组合索引"}]},{"ID":"20220919212150-3xgzr3q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220919212150-3xgzr3q","updated":"20220919212150"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20220919212150-9nom2fx.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20220922104604-8peshe4","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220922104604-8peshe4","updated":"20220922104845"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"身份证号和性别哪个加索引？"}]},{"ID":"20220922104848-koxheab","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220922104848-koxheab","updated":"20220922104906"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"like哪个会查全表？"}]},{"ID":"20220922105040-kxwi20m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220922105040-kxwi20m","updated":"20220922105041"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20220922105041-c9wocpy.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20220922105756-mycafzn","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220922105756-mycafzn","updated":"20220922105808"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"b+树？"}]},{"ID":"20221008090454-nay2xdu","Type":"NodeIFrame","Data":"\u003ciframe src=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/dalianpai/p/14372807.html\" data-src=\"\" border=\"0\" frameborder=\"no\" framespacing=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"width: 930px; height: 580px;\"\u003e\u003c/iframe\u003e","Properties":{"id":"20221008090454-nay2xdu","updated":"20221008090501"}},{"ID":"20221008150707-gxxsb4k","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20221008150707-gxxsb4k","updated":"20221008150734"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"MySQL中的四种隔离级别"}]},{"ID":"20221008150713-0ypsbjt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008150713-0ypsbjt","updated":"20221008150714"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20221008150714-ipjukt5.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20221008103128-j42p8ts","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20221008103128-j42p8ts","updated":"20221008103151"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"mysql一级缓存二级缓存"}]},{"ID":"20221009115601-7d3c4pc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221009115601-7d3c4pc","updated":"20221009115601"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"一级缓存："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\n一级缓存也称本地缓存，session级别的缓存，一级缓存是默认开启的，与数据库同一次的会话期间查询到的数据会放在本地缓存中，如果有需要获取相同的数据，则直接从缓存中取，就不会再次查询数据库。在日常的开发中，经常会有相同的sql执行多次的情况，mybatis就提供了一级缓存来优化这些查询，避免多次请求数据库，重点是它的作用域为一次sqlSession会话。"}]},{"ID":"20221009115601-nzlwly4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221009115601-nzlwly4","updated":"20221009115601"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"二级缓存："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\n二级缓存是全局缓存，是一个基于namespace级别的缓存，作用域更为广泛，不局限于一个sqlSession，可以在多个sqlSession之间共享，mybatis的二级缓存默认也是开启的，但是由于它的作用域是namespace，所以还需要在mapper.xml中开启才能生效，只需要加入cache标签即可。当要访问数据库形成一个会话查询一条数据时，这个数据就会被放在当前会话的一级缓存中，如果这个时候会话关闭了，那么以及缓存中的数据会被保存到二级缓存中，新的会话查询信息就会参照二级缓存，需要注意的是不同的namespaace会被防止到自己对应的缓存中去。\n"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"小结："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\n简单来说就是缓存首先一进来，就会先去二级缓存中查询，如果没有就去一级缓存中查找，一级缓存中没有的话，最后进入数据库中查找。作用顺序为二级缓存\u003e一级缓存\u003e数据库。需要注意的是，一级缓存作用域仅限于同一sqlSession中，无法感知到其他sqlSession中的数据变更，所以极易产生脏数据，而二级缓存可以通过cache-ref让多个mapper.xml共享一个namespace，从而实现缓存共享，但多表联动查询的时候会比较麻烦，由此，在生产环境的时候可以关闭一级缓存（statement级别），有需要的话可以打开二级缓存。如果是分布式应用的话， 这里我们不建议开启，具体原因大家可以了解一下哟~"}]},{"ID":"20221008082810-1husogm","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20221008082810-1husogm","updated":"20221008101933"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"原子性和一致性的区别"}]},{"ID":"20221008102037-thlx7yw","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20221008102037-thlx7yw","updated":"20221008102038"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20221008102038-bgiewyg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221008102038-bgiewyg","updated":"20221008102038"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一致性和原子性的区别是：一致性强调的最终状态，要么是初始状态（有可能事务回滚了），要么是最终状态，事务成功执行后；原子性强调的是操作的完整性，连续的操作不可分割，要么全部成功，要么全部失败"}]}]},{"ID":"20221008102007-ugvf5jw","Type":"NodeIFrame","Data":"\u003ciframe src=\"https://blog.csdn.net/qq_32069155/article/details/100902969?ops_request_misc=\u0026amp;request_id=\u0026amp;biz_id=102\u0026amp;utm_term=%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4%E6%80%A7%E5%92%8C%E5%8E%9F%E5%AD%90%E6%80%A7%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB\u0026amp;utm_medium=distribute.pc_search_result.none-task-blog-2~all~sobaiduweb~default-1-100902969.142^v51^pc_rank_34_queryrelevant25,201^v3^add_ask\u0026amp;spm=1018.2226.3001.4187\" data-src=\"\" border=\"0\" frameborder=\"no\" framespacing=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"width: 1311px; height: 668px;\"\u003e\u003c/iframe\u003e","Properties":{"id":"20221008102007-ugvf5jw","updated":"20221008102011"}},{"ID":"20221008082403-bwls94r","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20221008082403-bwls94r","updated":"20221008082420"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"MongoDB"}]},{"ID":"20221006101026-h3oxxcg","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20221006101026-h3oxxcg","updated":"20221006101035"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"用户表如何加权限"}]},{"ID":"20221027161003-1d1pjw1","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20221027161003-1d1pjw1","updated":"20221027161214"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20221027161005-wr9rebo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221027161005-wr9rebo","updated":"20221027161005"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON mydb.* to 'myuser'@'%';"}]},{"ID":"20221027161005-0xz7cma","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221027161005-0xz7cma","updated":"20221027161005"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"ALL代表所有权限，也可以选择增删改查等权限，小项目嫌麻烦，所以选择ALL"}]},{"ID":"20221027161005-sbwb1sj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221027161005-sbwb1sj","updated":"20221027161005"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"mydb是数据库的名称，您可更改为你自己数据库名称"}]},{"ID":"20221027161005-njoa9zw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221027161005-njoa9zw","updated":"20221027161005"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"myuser是数据库用户，您可更改为自己的数据库用户"}]},{"ID":"20221027161005-e25h81s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221027161005-e25h81s","updated":"20221027161005"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"%代表所有IP都能访问，您可更改为某个IP才能访问"}]}]},{"ID":"20221027161215-fngnvdm","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20221027161215-fngnvdm","updated":"20221027161221"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"正确的定义方法是"}]},{"ID":"20221027161215-kqpobel","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20221027161215-kqpobel","updated":"20221027161215"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"c2Nzcw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"grant [权限1，权限2...] on 某库.某表 to 新用户名@'主机名/IP地址' identified by '密码';\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20221027161215-ohsk5mr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221027161215-ohsk5mr","updated":"20221027161215"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们可以定义一个用户并让他拥有所有库，所有表的所有增删改查等操作权限，语句如下："}]},{"ID":"20221027161215-ims2bk8","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20221027161215-ims2bk8","updated":"20221027161215"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"c2Nzcw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"grant all on *.* to hehe@'localhost' identified by '123456';\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20221027161215-lyt89ue","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20221027161215-lyt89ue","updated":"20221027161215"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20221027161215-q33n00h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221027161215-q33n00h","updated":"20221027161215"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果要删除这个用户，用delete语句就可以了。"}]},{"ID":"20221027161215-d3abkv5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221027161215-d3abkv5","updated":"20221027161215"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"②库权限的控制：我们可以定义用户可以操作的库，只需要在上面的语句中，改各参数即可，你可能已经猜到了：上面语句中的\"某库\"修改成对应的库名即可。例如，给hehe用户赋予操作test库的所有权限："}]}]},{"ID":"20221027161215-m98yclx","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20221027161215-m98yclx","updated":"20221027161215"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"c2Nzcw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"grant all on test.* to hehe@'localhost' identified by '123456';\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20221027161215-9sjshd0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221027161215-9sjshd0","updated":"20221027161215"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"③精细到对表的权限的控制：改一下\"某表\"和\"权限X\"就可以了。例如：定义给用户hehe操作test库的goods表的insert，select，update的权限，代码如下："}]},{"ID":"20221027161215-bnbsmw6","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20221027161215-bnbsmw6","updated":"20221027161215"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"c3Fs"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"grant insert,select,update on test.goods to hehe@'localhost' identified by '123456';\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20221027161215-nmxkvvh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221027161215-nmxkvvh","updated":"20221027161215"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"最后，怎样回收用户的库级和表级权限呢？语法如下："}]},{"ID":"20221027161215-4f720ju","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20221027161215-4f720ju","updated":"20221027161215"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"c2Nzcw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"revoke [权限1，权限2...] on 某库.某表 from 用户名@'主机名/IP';\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20221027161215-maiiodr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221027161215-maiiodr","updated":"20221027161215"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"例如：回收用户hehe对test库的所有表的update的权限："}]},{"ID":"20221027161215-5tflzls","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20221027161215-5tflzls","updated":"20221027161215"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"c3Fs"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"revoke update on test.* from hehe@'localhost';\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20221011144804-3jm20y8","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20221011144804-3jm20y8","updated":"20221011144806"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雪花算法"}]},{"ID":"20221012114429-tosawd3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221012114429-tosawd3","updated":"20221012114430"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20221012114429-t51ynlx.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20221012114337-ctogvm1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221012114337-ctogvm1","updated":"20221012114338"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20221012114338-v3epnpb.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20221010145712-qr9fz8r","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20221010145712-qr9fz8r","updated":"20221010145846"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"索引优化"}]},{"ID":"20221010163931-t6do4gg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221010163931-t6do4gg","updated":"20221010163931"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果你在面试中，听到MySQL5.6”、“索引优化” 之类的词语，你就要立马get到，这个问的是“索引下推”。"}]},{"ID":"20221010163931-8wdyckf","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20221010163931-8wdyckf","updated":"20221010163931"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"什么是索引下推"}]},{"ID":"20221010163931-vuyavrx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221010163931-vuyavrx","updated":"20221010163931"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"索引下推(Index Condition Pushdown，简称ICP)，是MySQL5.6版本的新特性，它能减少回表查询次数，提高查询效率。"}]},{"ID":"20221010163931-etb2bwc","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20221010163931-etb2bwc","updated":"20221010163931"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"索引下推优化的原理"}]},{"ID":"20221010163931-yzzbmqe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221010163931-yzzbmqe","updated":"20221010163931"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们先简单了解一下MySQL大概的架构："}]},{"ID":"20221010163931-ugibxq2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221010163931-ugibxq2","updated":"20221010163931"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"MySQL大概架构"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://p3-juejin.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-k3u1fbpfcp/52288fa925f84cef937bb0b46d27c60a~tplv-k3u1fbpfcp-zoom-in-crop-mark:4536:0:0:0.image"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20221010163931-7v4dr9o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221010163931-7v4dr9o","updated":"20221010163931"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"MySQL服务层负责SQL语法解析、生成执行计划等，并调用存储引擎层去执行数据的存储和检索。"}]},{"ID":"20221010163931-va74wx3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20221010163